Text: The relationships between the mumbo-jumbo and the morons. Priceless.

What utter crap. As a 45 year old witch from a family of witches from a clan of witches I can tell you that none of our oral or written history shows any organized contact with the Illuminati. The sole resemblance between us is secrecy. Organized Witchcraft is a contradiction in terms, whereas The fabled Illuminati are nothing but organized.
